      "id": "effect-index-determinism",
      "description": "M32: tusq effect index --json produces byte-identical output across three runs on the same manifest; side_effect_class bucket-key enum is closed (four values); aggregation_key enum is closed (two values); bucket iteration order is the frozen closed-enum order (read → write → destructive → unknown)",
      "scenario_type": "effect_index_determinism",
      "synthetic_capabilities": [
        {
          "name": "list_users",
